  "method": [
    "Preheat the oven to 300°F.",
    "Mix all the ingredients together except for the raisins. Spread out in a large baking pan.",
    "Bake for 40 minutes. Take out of the oven every 10 minutes and stir. Return to the oven.",
    "After 30 minutes, add raisins and stir. Bake for 10 more minutes. Take out of the oven and let cool.",
    "Pack in airtight container. Will keep for 4 weeks."
